{"tid":1299002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HK Express話我國籍喺大陸喎 睇嚟好快變香港市啦","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:31:08.000Z","uid":194218,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62ebf6bd95a313ef5861734169d8ef46a41b881c","tid":1299002,"uid":194218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 真喺好燥<br />\n事緣我呢幾日去咗旅行<br />\n聽日返香港，就諗住check in回程班機啦<br />\n點知一開嗰app，我朋友嗰國藉無啦啦變咗大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XebOViN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXebOViN.png&h=d6a90eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己用BNO所以冇問題<br />\n但我明明去程check in喺肯定幫我朋友剔咗HKSAR<br />\n當我質問customer service嘅時候佢竟然屈我喺我自己揀mainland China<br />\n真喺好不安，喺咪HK express想搶先一步宣布香港特別行政區已經消失，正式成為中國香港市？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrSB4e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrSB4e5.png&h=07a9441a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVbnZOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVbnZOq.png&h=28b763c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Knj5c8q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnj5c8q.png&h=862c89b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2hVAmM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2hVAmM.png&h=88b27765&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7286e99e5165db2e1e5fd5f54f0aafb7b1d5620a","tid":1299002,"uid":194218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62ebf6bd95a313ef5861734169d8ef46a41b881c","tid":1299002,"uid":194218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 真喺好燥<br />\n事緣我呢幾日去咗旅行<br />\n聽日返香港，就諗住check in回程班機啦<br />\n點知一開嗰app，我朋友嗰國藉無啦啦變咗大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\